  "detailed_description": "<h1>⚔️🐸♟️MY OTHER GAMES! ⚔️🐸♟️</h1><p><table>\t<tr>\t\t<td></td>\t\t<td></td></tr></table></p><br><h1>-</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>[/url]\n\n\n[b]ABOUT THIS GAME[/b]\n\nHelp Raven reach the top of the tower, restoring equilibrium and saving the world from oblivion.\n\n[imgvid poster.avif=\"\" webm=\"\" mp4=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"578\"][/imgvid]\n\nTrust on your reflexes or find the safest way through every room, collect all the gems and get out. Who knows what to expect in the next trial?\n\n[imgvid poster.avif=\"\" webm=\"\" mp4=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"576\"][/imgvid]\n\n60+ handcrafted open-ended levels spread through 4 stages filled with puzzles, combat with a dynamic soundtrack by Vincent Colavita.\n\n[imgvid poster.avif=\"\" webm=\"\" mp4=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"552\"][/imgvid<br><br><br><strong>ABOUT THIS GAME</strong><br><br>Help Raven reach the top of the tower, restoring equilibrium and saving the world from oblivion.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1689270/extras/b06826820519cbf280dac1714269bbf0.poster.avif?t=1687885261\" width=600 height=578 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1689270/extras/b06826820519cbf280dac1714269bbf0.webm?t=1687885261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1689270/extras/b06826820519cbf280dac1714269bbf0.mp4?t=1687885261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Trust on your reflexes or find the safest way through every room, collect all the gems and get out. Who knows what to expect in the next trial?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1689270/extras/825b9c9a0437709b498a445115f9e33e.poster.avif?t=16